824
00:54:26,430 --> 00:54:29,330
Not only does he stay on my girl's mind,

825
00:54:29,330 --> 00:54:31,894
he also stays in contact with her.

826
00:54:31,894 --> 00:54:35,596
Do I have to understand that as well?

827
00:54:35,596 --> 00:54:39,270
But they say there's nothing between them anymore.

828
00:54:39,270 --> 00:54:40,520
