Joon.

854
00:56:23,980 --> 00:56:25,480
You're a big star.

855
00:56:25,480 --> 00:56:27,218
Be careful out on the street.

856
00:56:27,218 --> 00:56:31,179
What do you mean? I'm going inside now anyway.

857
00:56:31,179 --> 00:56:34,270
By the way, I'll go to Japan tomorrow.

858
00:56:34,270 --> 00:56:38,330
When I come back, let's meet those men from that reunion.

859
00:56:38,330 --> 00:56:39,979
Yes. Have a good trip.

860
00:56:39,979 --> 00:56:40,770
Good night.

861
00:56:40,770 --> 00:56:42,730
Bye.

862
